{"tid":1651642,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"D分化引戰post，係所有連登仔一手一腳推上熱門既，比五毛利用咗都唔知","createTime":"2019-10-13T11:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T02:36:53.000Z","uid":190579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d04c146d64a22439bbca2b9f7ed033288c7bd8b5","tid":1651642,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"問題大家都知唔使講，我只講<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解決方案</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n連登改咗新規距<br />\n大家既習慣都要變<br />\n善用全新「推」和「拉」</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱門準則之「推」</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">單一用戶 (Unique User) 的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>觀看次數</strong></span>及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">停留時間</span></strong>。</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n因為你哋入到緊要post，花半秒回個「推」，就一世都唔返入去<br />\n要個post keep住浮，係要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同一個人</span></strong>不斷入番個post <br />\n所以大家唔好淨係推，要入去<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>留低一齊討論</strong></span>，集思廣益。睇埋下面留言，睇下樓主係唔係標題黨同fake news撚<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱門準則之「拉」</span></span> </strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>不推文回覆數量：例如在一個主題中如有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大量會員使用不推文回覆</span></strong>，將會大幅減低熱門分數。</ins></span><br />\n因為有人討論廢post 時唔用不推文。<br />\n如果你想佢沉，唔係要留低同佢罵戰，咁樣會推咗post <span style=\"font-size: small;\">(睇番上面)</span><br />\n亦都唔係要離開個post，應該要入去<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用不推文，回個「拉」</strong></span>，再快快頭也不回走人，唔再入番個post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[公告] LIHKG 常見問題公告 2019-09-25<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n大家幫手<br />\n用正確既方法<br />\n將此post 推上熱門</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5765d490797ace4b4cf9445e8048cb5bd7a7c3b3","tid":1651642,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc1d1f1c33103d1837f9e9da966b5c5a412a535","tid":1651642,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983761b06b2a33b724ccb8b20bfeb5ba318c82d7","tid":1651642,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4a576f7d14804f117adfd700b8e882aa379d53","tid":1651642,"uid":131148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"試下先<br />\n推"},{"pid":"b10558f785e030ff4033256b41fe354d778a1d7e","tid":1651642,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb4a576f7d14804f117adfd700b8e882aa379d53","tid":1651642,"uid":131148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"試下先<br />\n推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a874b844b8caf3052db5190261b531c787e418d8","tid":1651642,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66321c91a5d558b143dca3f1683b9cb88182dd0","tid":1651642,"uid":215894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"本人正式宣布發起不自殺聲明運動!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/165